name: PixelFem #42 - Dian Fossey
description:
Primatologist Dian Fossey has become a conservation legend. The videos captured by National Geographic enchanted audiences and motivated them to care about mountain gorillas. Dian Fossey told the world how mountain gorillas live, and fought tooth and nail to save them.

✺This work is part of PixelFems, an evolving project on the Tezos blockchain celebrating iconic women from the past and present✺
